'''Lorenzo Schneider''' (August 30, 1925 - June 13, 2021) was an Austrian-American actor, bodybuilder and politician who served as Governor of New York from 1977 to 1985.

==Early Life and coming to America==
The result of a random hookup, Lorenzo was born in Vienna, the son of travel agent Marco Schnider (1901 - 1993) and wedding planner Nina Lang (1898 - 1989). 

